fields.physical_description:
A white, shiny card portfolio containing photocopies of  forty photcopies of fashion designs, including samples of leather and textiles, one card folder entitled '2000' and a postcard.  The Antoni * Alison logo is on the front of the portfolio and is printed in blue ink.
[drawing] Postcard in plain greenish-blue inscribed with the word 'Trendy' in black.
[drawing] Postcard in plain greenish-blue inscribed with the word 'Trendy' in black.
[drawing] An A4 sheet of CAD print out depicting dark, irregular shapes of beef burgers on a grey ground,.  Two samples of fabric and a fluorescent green piece of paper are attached.
[drawing] A4 sheet of paper with a CAD design for the decoration across the chest of a T-shirt consisting of a rectangle within which is a row of peas .  There is a sample of bright green sticky paper and two textile samples each in a different shade of brown.  The samples are attached to the top left corner.
[drawing] A4 sheet of paper with a CAD design of two T-shirts.  One T-shirt is white and has a design of a row of peas across the chest.  The other T-shirt is dark with two burgers on the chest.
[drawing] An A4 sized sheet of paper with a CAD print out of five squares incorporating respectively a star burst, the date '2000', the words 'Ha ha ha', a smiling face and a blob with a face.
[drawing] An A4 sized piece of paper with a CAD print out of a square incorporating a smiling face with one of the wide-open eyes upside down.
[drawing] An A4 sized piece of paper with a CAD print out of four squares depicting three, different smiling faces and a blob with a face.
[drawing] An A4 sized piece of paper with a CAD print out of two smiling faces below which are inscriptions.
[drawing] An A4 sized sheet of paper with CAD print out of a square incorporating a smiling face with closed eyes bordered by long lashes.  There is an inscription and the designers' company logo beneath the square. Textile samples one of pink and the other of brown fringe are attaced to the top right corner.
[drawing] An A4 sized piece of paper with a CAD print out of a line drawing of a T-shirt incorporating two squares, on the chest, containing smiuling faces.
[drawing] An A4 sized piece of paper with a CAD print out of a line drawing of a T_shirt incorporating a square, on the chest, containing a smiling face with open eyes, one of which is upside down.
[drawing] Anm A4 sized piece of paper with a CAD print out of line drawing of  a T-shirt incorporating a square, over the chest, depicting a smiling face with two closed eyes with long lashes below which is an inscription and the designers' logo.
[drawing] An A4 sized piece of paper with a CAD print out of the line drawing of a T-shirt neckline and the outline of its shoulders.  There are five squares at the bottom of the sheet of paper containing respectively a star burst, the date '2000', an inscription, a smiling face and a blob with a smiling face.
[drawing] A4 sheet of paper with a starburst in which is the inscription '34p'.  There is a fluorescent sticky label and a sample of bright pink sticky paper beneath which are two samples of synthetic leather each in a different shade of brown.
[drawing] A4 sheet of paper with a CAD design of a 'V' necked T-shirt with a starburst in which is the inscription 34p.
[drawing] A4 sheet of paper with a list of model numbers (presumably for designs for T-shirts) and their inscriptions.
[drawing] A4 sheet of paper with typography for an inscription for a T-shirt design.
[drawing] A4 sheet of paper with typography for an inscription for a T-shirt design.
[drawing] A4 sheet of paper with typography for an inscription for a T-shirt design.
[drawing] A4 sheet of paper with typography for an inscription for a T-shirt design.
[drawing] A4 sheet of paper with typography for an inscription for a T-shirt.
[drawing] A4 sheet of paper with CAD design of a tiny design for a T-shirt in the bottom left corner.
[drawing] A4 sheet of paper with a CAD design of three T-shirts each with a different inscription as decoration.
[drawing] A4 sheet of paper with a CAD design of three T-shirts each with a different inscription as decoration.
[drawing] A4 sheet of paper with a CAD design of decoration for beneath the neckline of a T-shirt in design E.677.5-1997.  The design consists of a triangular shape with rounded corners within which is a circle like an egg-yolk.
[drawing] A4 sheet of paper with a CAD design of a 'V' shape for the decoration beneath the neckline of a T-shirt in design E.677.5-1997.  There is a sample of fabric in the bottom right corner.  The fabric is black and has a sparkling surface.
[drawing] A4 sheet of paper with a CAD design of a four-sided figure like a bar which is the design for decoration beneath the 'V' neckline of one of the T-shirts on design E.677.5-1997.
[drawing] A4 sheet of paper with a CAD design of a zigzag which is the design for decoration beneath the 'V' neck of one of the T-shirts in E.677.5-1977.
[drawing] A4 sheet of paper with a CAD design of four T-shirts with 'V' necks and a different design beneath each of their necklines.
[drawing] A4 sheet of paper with a CAD design incorporating the date '2000', a star burst surrounding the inscription and the Antoni & Alison logo.
[drawing] A4 sheet of paper with a CAD design incorporating the date '2000', a star burst surrounding an inscription and the Antoni & Alison logo.
[drawing] White card folder on which a rectangular piece of paper is pasted across the fold. The date '2000' is printed onto the piece of paper. In the last '0' of '2000' is part of a gilded metal stud on a red ground.  It appears like an eye peeping out.  It is part of the front of a badge, complete with safety pin, the bulk of which is attached to the back of the folder with pieces of adhesive paper.
